<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          background-color: #121212;
          color: #ffffff;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
          max-width: 100%;
          margin: 50px auto;
          padding: 20px;
          background-color: #1e1e1e;
          border-radius: 10px;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
          text-align: center;
        }
        .email-header img {
          width: 50px;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
          color: #ffcc00;
          margin: 10px 0 5px;
        }
        .email-header p {
          font-size: 16px;
          color: #aaaaaa;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .email-content p {
          font-size: 14px;
          color: #cccccc;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .email-content .code-box {
          display: inline-block;
          padding: 15px 30px;
          font-size: 24px;
          font-weight: bold;
          color: #ffcc00;
          background-color: #2c3333;
          border-radius: 5px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .email-footer p {
          font-size: 12px;
          color: #666666;
          margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Auth</h1>
        <p>Two-Factor Authentication</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-content">
        <p>Hi there! Use the code below to complete your login process:</p>
        <div class="code-box">{{verificationCode}}</div>
        <p>This code will expire in {{expiryTime}} minutes. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
        <p>Â© 2024 Auth App. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>